"Autorización Electrónico)` và mã QR để xác thực an toàn."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/argentina.rst:39
msgid ""
"**Secure storage and retrieval**: Complying with Argentina’s ten-year "
