#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices/electronic_invoicing/mexico.rst:20
msgid ""
"**Digital tax receipt validation**: All :abbr:`CFDIs (Comprobante Fiscal "
"Digital por Internet)` must be digitally signed and validated by :abbr:`SAT "
