"To add another :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution`, click on the line to "
"reveal the :guilabel:`Analytic` pop-over window. Click :guilabel:`Add a "
"line`, then select the desired :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` from the "
"drop-down field."
