#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:786
msgid ""
"Choose the *SRI Payment Method* for each payment method's configuration."
msgstr "Zvolte *Platební metodu SRI* v nastavení každé platební metody."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/ecuador.rst:787
msgid ""
"Customers can manually input their identification type and number during "
"eCommerce checkout."
msgstr ""
"Zákazníci mohou během placení v elektronickém obchodu ručně zadat svůj typ a "
