"In the :guilabel:`Create new webhook` popup, click :guilabel:`Add` on to "
"the :guilabel:`Standard webhook` line."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/finance/payment_providers/adyen.rst:41
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Webhook generation` form, in the :guilabel:`Server "
"configuration` section, enter your Odoo database :guilabel:`URL` followed by "
"`/payment/adyen/notification`."
msgstr ""
"Trên biểu mẫu :guilabel:`Tạo webhook`, trong phần :guilabel:`Cấu hình máy "
